label: containedTransportEquipment
comment: A piece of transport equipment contained within this piece of logistics transport equipment, such as a pallet.

rangeIncludes.comment: A piece of transport equipment that is associated with another piece of transport equipment, such as a maritime container placed on a rail wagon for transportation.

domainIncludes.comment: A piece of equipment used to hold, protect or secure cargo for logistics purposes.,A referenced piece of equipment used to hold, protect or secure cargo for logistics purposes.
